  "prompt": "Is taking supplements like Nutrilite useful or do they have side effects?",
  "response": "Nutrilite supplements can be beneficial for some people, but there are pros and cons to consider:\n\nPotential Benefits:\n1. May help fill nutritional gaps\n2. Can support overall health and wellness\n3. Some supplements target specific nutritional needs\n4. Produced by a reputable company (Amway)\n\nPotential Drawbacks/Side Effects:\n1. Not all supplements are FDA-regulated\n2. Possible interactions with medications\n3. Some people may experience side effects like:\n- Digestive issues\n- Allergic reactions\n- Headaches\n- Nausea\n\nRecommendations:\n1. Consult with a healthcare professional before starting any supplement\n2. Get nutrients primarily from a balanced diet\n3. Be aware of your individual health needs\n4. Choose high-quality supplements\n5. Follow recommended dosages\n\nIndividual results can vary, so what works for one person might not work the same for another. Always prioritize a balanced diet and professional medical advice.",
